---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import ServicePage from '../templates/service/ServicePage.astro'
import ServiceSection from '../templates/service/ServiceSection.astro'
---

<ServicePage
  title="Home Help Services | Maggi Maid Support in Bradford"
  description="Discover reliable home help services from Maggi Maid in Bradford. One-to-one support with daily tasks to help seniors stay safe and independent at home."
>
  <Fragment slot="hero-image">
    <Image
      src={import('../assets/images/hero-image-1.png')}
      alt="A senior lady smiling and talking with her companion."
      loading="eager"
    />
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="heading">
    <span class="font-italic font-normal">Home Help Services</span> in Bradford
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="hero-content">
    Struggling with daily tasks? Whether you're a senior who wants to keep your
    independence or a family member worried about a loved one at home, I get it.
    My elderly home help services provide the practical support you need to stay
    independent at home—from light housekeeping to meal prep and shopping. With
    over 30 years of childminding experience and full DBS clearance, I bring a
    trusted, personal approach to senior care—offering one-to-one support you
    can rely on, without the worry of strangers coming and going.
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="services">
    <ServiceSection
      id="light-domestic-cleaning-services"
      number="01"
      heading="Light Domestic Cleaning Services"
    >
      <Fragment slot="description">
        Keep your home fresh and comfortable with reliable cleaning support
        tailored for seniors. I provide thorough elderly house cleaning
        services, including
        <span class="font-semibold">vacuuming, dusting, and mopping</span>
        to maintain a tidy living space. You'll also get help with
        <span class="font-semibold">
          bed linen changes, clutter management, and kitchen and bathroom
          sanitizing
        </span>—all done with care and attention to your preferences. No
        rotating strangers, just consistent, respectful assistance so your home
        stays clean and welcoming.
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="image">
        <Image
          src={import('../assets/images/light-domestic-cleaning-services.jpg')}
          alt="Light domestic cleaning services"
        />
      </Fragment>
    </ServiceSection>

    <ServiceSection
      id="laundry-and-ironing-help"
      number="02"
      heading="Laundry & Ironing Help"
    >
      <Fragment slot="description">
        Enjoy fresh, neatly cared-for clothes without the hassle. My laundry and
        ironing services for seniors take care of everything—from
        <span class="font-semibold">washing</span>
        and
        <span class="font-semibold">drying</span>
        to
        <span class="font-semibold">folding</span>
        and
        <span class="font-semibold">putting away your laundry</span>, all done
        in the comfort of your own home. I provide thorough ironing so your
        clothes look their best, while always respecting your preferences. No
        heavy lifting or tedious chores—just reliable help to keep your wardrobe
        tidy and organized. I do not take laundry off-site; all washing and
        ironing is done in your home for your convenience and peace of mind.
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="image">
        <Image
          src={import('../assets/images/laundry-and-ironing-help.jpg')}
          alt="laundry and ironing help"
        />
      </Fragment>
    </ServiceSection>

    <ServiceSection
      id="personalised-meal-preparation"
      number="03"
      heading="Personalised Meal Preparation"
    >
      <Fragment slot="description">
        Enjoy <span class="font-semibold">
          delicious, nutritious meals prepared
        </span> just the way you like them—right in your
        <span class="font-semibold">own kitchen</span>. My meal preparation
        service for seniors focuses on creating dishes that suit your tastes,
        dietary needs, and appetite. Whether it's adapting family recipes to be
        easier to eat or ensuring meals are stored safely for later, I handle
        everything with proper
        <span class="font-semibold">food hygiene certification</span>
        and care.
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="image">
        <Image
          src={import('../assets/images/personalised-meal-preparation.jpg')}
          alt="Personalised meal preparation"
        />
      </Fragment>
    </ServiceSection>

    <ServiceSection
      id="grocery-shopping-and-errands"
      number="04"
      heading="Grocery Shopping & Errands"
    >
      <Fragment slot="description">
        Let me handle your essential errands so you can skip the stress. My
        grocery shopping and assistance service covers everything from
        supermarket runs to
        <span class="font-semibold">prescription pickups</span>
        and
        <span class="font-semibold">post office visits</span>. I'll carefully
        select fresh produce, check expiry dates, and even carry heavy
        bags—because no one should struggle with basic necessities. Need your
        <span class="font-semibold">pension collected</span> or a
        <span class="font-semibold">parcel posted</span>? Consider it done. With
        DBS-checked reliability and local knowledge of Bradford shops, I make
        sure your errands are completed efficiently, just the way you'd do them
        yourself.
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="image">
        <Image
          src={import('../assets/images/grocery-shopping-and-errands.jpg')}
          alt="Grocery shopping and errands"
        />
      </Fragment>
    </ServiceSection>
  </Fragment>
</ServicePage>
